### 1. GET available vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### 2. GET shipments filtered by status "InTransit"
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### 3. GET all shipments for a specific customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Shipments?$filter=customerId eq a101ade3-2222-4000-c000-000000000001

### 4. POST a new shipment booking
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
    "customerId": "a101ade3-2222-4000-c000-000000000001",
    "pickupCity": "Hyderabad",
    "deliveryCity": "Bangalore",
    "weight": 15.5,
    "charges": 500.00
}

### 5. PATCH shipment status to "Delivered" and set deliveredAt
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Shipments(ID=ENTER_SHIPMENT_UUID_HERE)
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "Delivered",
    "deliveredAt": "2026-05-31T10:00:00Z"
}

### 6. GET routes between two cities
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Hyderabad' and toCity eq 'Bangalore'

### 7. GET drivers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics-service/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc
